1. *Rez* u nozi mu se otvorio kad se spotakao. (Cut, The cut in his leg opened when he stumbled.)
2. Moram da napravim *rez* u budžetu za ovaj mesec. (Cut, I have to make a cut in the budget for this month.)
3. *Rez* na tom nožu je previše tup. (Edge, The edge on that knife is too dull.)
4. *Rez* je bio savršeno kuvan, baš onako kako volim. (Steak, The steak was perfectly cooked, just the way I like it.)
5. Kada se odlučio za novu tetovažu, pitao je majstora da napravi *rez* na drugačiji način. (Incision, When he decided on a new tattoo, he asked the artist to make the incision in a different way.)
6. Ne mogu da poverujem da je naš tim doživeo takav *rez* u ovom meču. (Defeat, I can't believe our team suffered such a defeat in this match.)
7. Kupio sam novi *rez* za moju testeru jer je stari bio oštećen. (Blade, I bought a new blade for my saw because the old one was damaged.)
8. Zbog velikog *reza* na proračunu, nećemo biti u mogućnosti da finansiramo sve projekte koje smo planirali. (Cut, Due to a large cut in the budget, we will not be able to finance all the projects we planned.)